bled, and you\'re not collecting new clicks.','In order to see the clicks, you need Relevanssi Premium.'=>'In order to see the clicks, you need Relevanssi Premium.','"Hits" is the average hits this search query has found.'=>'"Hits" é a média de acessos que essa consulta de pesquisa encontrou.','Successful searches'=>'Successful searches','Searches that found nothing'=>'Searches that found nothing','# of Searches'=>'# Número de pesquisas','All history'=>'All history','7 days'=>'7 dias','Last week'=>'Last week','This week'=>'This week','30 days'=>'30 dias','Last month'=>'Último mês','This month'=>'This month','Year so far'=>'Year so far','Filter'=>'Filtro','To:'=>'Para:','From:'=>'De:','You are using Polylang and are in "Show all languages" mode. Please select a language before adjusting the synonym settings.'=>'You are using Polylang and are in "Show all languages" mode. Please select a language before adjusting the synonym settings.','If you want to use synonyms in AND searches, enable synonym indexing on the Indexing tab. Also, any changes to the synonyms won\'t take effect until you rebuild the index.'=>'If you want to use synonyms in AND searches, enable synonym indexing on the Indexing tab. Also, any changes to the synonyms won\'t take effect until you rebuild the index.','You are using Polylang and are in "Show all languages" mode. Please select a language before adjusting the stopword settings.'=>'You are using Polylang and are in "Show all languages" mode. Please select a language before adjusting the stopword settings.','Users'=>'Usuários','Relevanssi Premium has a click tracking feature where you can track which posts are clicked from the search results. That way you can tell what is your most interesting content and how the search is actually used to access posts.'=>'Relevanssi Premium has a click tracking feature where you can track which posts are clicked from the search results. That way you can tell what is your most interesting content and how the sea