st is not indexed','Nothing found for ID %d.'=>'Nothing found for ID %d.','When a highlight matches part of the word, if this option is enabled, the highlight will be expanded to highlight the whole word.'=>'When a highlight matches part of the word, if this option is enabled, the highlight will be expanded to highlight the whole word.','Expand highlights to cover full words'=>'Expand highlights to cover full words','Expand highlights'=>'Expand highlights','Check the post'=>'Check the post','In Relevanssi Premium, you can find this feature for each post on the post edit page. %1$sBuy Relevanssi Premium here%2$s.'=>'In Relevanssi Premium, you can find this feature for each post on the post edit page. %1$sBuy Relevanssi Premium here%2$s.','In order to figure out problems with indexing posts, you can test how Relevanssi sees the post by entering the post ID number in the field below.'=>'In order to figure out problems with indexing posts, you can test how Relevanssi sees the post by entering the post ID number in the field below.','Debugging'=>'Debugging','These values may be inaccurate. If you need exact values, %1$supdate the counts%2$s'=>'These values may be inaccurate. If you need exact values, %1$supdate the counts%2$s','Blocked by a filter function'=>'Bloqueado por uma função de filtro','Relevanssi index exclude'=>'Relevanssi index exclude','Add default stopwords'=>'Adicionar stopwords padrão','Added stopwords from the stopword file.'=>'Added stopwords from the stopword file.','Couldn\'t read the stopwords from the file.'=>'Couldn\'t read the stopwords from the file.','The stopword file for the language \'%s\' doesn\'t exist.'=>'The stopword file for the language \'%s\' doesn\'t exist.','Added stopwords from the database.'=>'Added stopwords from the database.','Taxonomy %s is public'=>'Taxonomy %s is public','Taxonomy %s is not public'=>'Taxonomy %s is not public','Index taxonomy %s'=>'Index taxonomy %s','For more detailed control over the attachment type indexin